    "This deficiency extends to other barriers, including cognitive and usability barriers as well as infrastructure barriers.",
    "Some believe that ethical AI principles alone are insufficient to ensure that companies use AI responsibly.",
    "Instead, a strict governance framework should be implemented to reduce AI-related risks (Eitel-Porter 2021).",
    "However, enforceable legal regulations for \"AI for all\" are largely absent.",
    "Even when focusing on domestic AI legislation across various countries, truly hard legal frameworks are rare, let alone regulations specifically promoting \"AI for all\"."
